Organizers of Big Brother Naija, BBNaija, on Friday issued a stern warning to housemates. The housemates were warned not to discuss their audition process any longer in the house. Neo, Trikytee and Kiddwaya in the kitchen on Friday morning were discussing about the audition. Biggie in the brief read by the Head of House, Erica said any more discussions about the audition will attract severe punishment. Erica said: ”Housemates are not to discuss their auditions any longer. “If they do, the punishment will be VERY severe.” Recall that the housemates were also warned days ago not to use the words ‘fans and votes’ in the house